{"type": "article", "id": 34598, "title": "把牙膏装进牙刷，其实一点也不难｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-17T23:28:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 954, "name": "Herman Miller"}, {"id": 16270, "name": "Industrial Facility"}, {"id": 34979, "name": "Tomogram"}, {"id": 34980, "name": "Alec Thibodeau"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 240, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161118072747GoURAWd02PYBvOJc.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Sona by Sona</h3><p>来自台湾的陈冠豪因为喜欢旅游加上曾经戴过牙套，有过餐餐牙刷牙膏不离身的经历，为了在减少环境污染的同时让有类似需求的人们减少包里的负担，他带领的设计团队研发了这款名为 Sona 的填充式牙刷。只需要把牙膏挤在握柄内部，牙膏就会在推钮的推动下从刷毛处流出。握柄内的结构在气压原理的作用下，只要不反向推动，清洗时水就不会流到牙刷里污染牙膏。握柄内最多能够容纳 15 毫升的牙膏，每天刷牙两次的情况下可以连续使用七天以上。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/sona\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为新台币 250 元，替换刷头（三个一组）的价格为 70 元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210748G4k2lNBS1C86sEK5.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661017\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210748iU42hvFpCeIaMZqo.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666102\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210756kq3LiETc1WVehJYu.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.661017\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210747fBWCA6m8DR7tQVcy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210746gnRaskFVqwoJ3jYE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>I Still See the X by Alec Thibodeau</h3><p>如果你对月相感兴趣，不妨来看看美国设计师 Alec Thibodeau 为 2017 年设计的月相日历 I Still See the X。之所以称为代表十的罗马数字 X，是因为 Thibodeau 自 2007 年起就开始制作月相日历了，而明年刚好是十周年。日历由罗德岛的 DWRI Letterpress 公司采用了凸版印刷技术制作，虽然它是根据东时区设计的，但只要在北半球，误差就会小于一天。你可以通过<a href=\"http://huetown.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买，售价为 40 美元。它限量一千张，每张都有 Thibodeau 手写的编号和签名。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210920crsYiymTDd9gN02o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.618000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611172109190AVQiHXPDbqK5msM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111721091958MhbDXAvk0aGqlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210919KghcpCaeuTfW3Zmq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.069000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Tomogram toys by Tomogram</h3><p>韩国 <a href=\"http://www.tomogram.kr/index.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tomogram</a> 工作室最近带来了一套由多种材料组合而成的 DIY 创意玩具，从最早的设计图来看，它就像是一只色彩斑澜的小鸭怪兽。玩具由四个易组装的部件组成，设计师希望通过不同材质或是颜色间的搭配，强调人的创造力与不同的个性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611172239025VATFnOiPCHGND67.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117223902aefyUXS9p1dKR5V2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117223902K4J7LZrtREjIwbfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117223903OpUZ8Gj3JzQv2W1k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117223903rC64G7BmRNfYjFIq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117223903WPO8AV7X9JmcU2Be.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><h3>Plex by Industrial Facility</h3><p>伦敦设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/tag/industrial-facility/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Industrial Facility</a> 最近为家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.hermanmiller.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Herman Miller</a> 设计了一套模块化的家具系列 Plex，囊括了包括扶手椅、沙发、长椅在内的各类座椅。除了模块化提供的极高的组合自由和延伸性之外，Plex 还拥有设有电源插口底座和可调节的头枕配件，无论是居家还是办公环境都很适用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117225123A0gVbPC7wJrEh96X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.850856\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117225123NR91kAjlTnJL4adH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740831\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117225124FZKtDV7IAgWeOXMQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117225124CNqhJO43scarfnWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749389\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117225123eUBKvrZSYGIhLDRV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.705379\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117225124VnyRgfA1U7iEJOrQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ljud by Fulden Dehneli</h3><p>这个名叫 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43696785/L-J-U-D\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ljud</a> 的扬声器是瑞典设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/fuldendehneli\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fulden Dehneli</a> 以北欧极简风格为灵感创作的概念产品。为了让设备能够更好地融入环境之中，Dehneli 摒弃了繁复的造型并采用了百搭的黑白单色。三层结构的 Ljud 上下各有一道凹痕，顶部专门用来放置触控式遥控器的凹槽也采用了相似的设计，营造出一种微妙的悬浮感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210624ougcy2X1GkAJnLsf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.569167\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210619RbUFXLfYQgOwKGe0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.513333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210627ajLeOEtqfIQPZ3BT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.569167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111721062420FKBovMiw3I7tSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.405833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Keep Me Together by Sean Mackey et al.</h3><p>美国佐治亚理工学院的五位学生在发现传统创可贴包装取用并不是非常方便后，设计了这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.cmeschia.com/portfolio/keep-me-together/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Keep Me Together</a> 的扁平化包装。根据不同需要，包装分为随身携带的 10、办公室的 30 和家中的 70 张三种容量。创可贴只有一端保留了保护膜，另一端则直接粘在包装内部，取用时只要轻轻一撕即可。为了进一步减轻对环境的影响，这套包装所使用的材料都是可回收和可降解的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210703N6nQ5yRhzkgJ4Dsm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639773\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611172107036UE9zna5TPoF3Hjc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210705RU0fPZH3erqJC5iw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210705zf2RdywlPFJ1TZD4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016111721070640sLqGQASip3XZVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667045\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161117210701EGbaK3ezdJg1VDlx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.639773\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}